**Capital Raising Announcement Summary:**  
- **Structure:** Institutional Placement  
- **Total Capital Raised:** AUD 203 million  
- **Issue Price:** AUD 4.20/share (2.2% premium to last close, 18.0% premium to 15-day VWAP).  
- **Settlement Date:** 31 July 2025; **Listing Date:** 1 August 2025.  
- **Pro-Forma Cash Balance:** AUD 288 million (post-placement).  

**Key Upcoming Catalysts:**  
- **Prostate Cancer Trials:**  
  - Co-PSMA trial readout (Q3/Q4 2025).  
  - Phase 3 trials (AMPLIFY/CLARIFY) completion (Q4 2025/H1 2026).  
- **Regulatory Milestones:** NDA submission planning for 64Cu-SAR-bisPSMA.  
- **Pipeline Progress:** First-in-human trials for breast cancer (64/67Cu-SAR-trastuzumab) and 64Cu-SAR-bisFAP (H2 2026).  

**Additional Material Note:**  
- Short interest in CU6 shares reached ~10% pre-placement.
